 />\n係2k meepo 永遠肥唔起"},{"pid":"ac2a94304ee202a8bfeea8dec8e3728e8fbdf6c7","tid":97000,"uid":78234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T13:00:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n不停分身個隻應該係Phantom Lancer<br />\nmeepo係E隻<br />\n<img src=\"https://hydra-media.cursecdn.com/dota2.gamepedia.com/0/03/Meepo.png?version=9e06da86a98ce5ef920561228f7680d1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhydra-media.cursecdn.com%2Fdota2.gamepedia.com%2F0%2F03%2FMeepo.png%3Fversion%3D9e06da86a98ce5ef920561228f7680d1&h=208a5b2c&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n2k 場見到依隻自動輸</blockquote><br />\n對家定自家先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nE個版本真係一個練佢既好日子(自帶吸血,閃避,龍心,A杖)<br />\n特別係冇咩人識counter佢<br />\nfarm個20-30分鐘就無敵</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打係應該高階場打<br />\n係2k meepo 永遠肥唔起</blockquote><br />\n我都係3-4k場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n打中單<br />\n除非對面好針對(1lv orge/bh掛你機,封曬你D野etc),唔係就好易肥<br />\n今個patch有火鍋去補狀態,所以就算中單打D比較強勢既英都唔會話farm唔起<br />\n3-5lv 開始線野雙收<br />\n2k場就打得獨食D,唔好亂參團<br />\n20-30分鐘 25lv帶rosh盾上高就無敵"},{"pid":"b165de06cf901fed3310d23ff7c7a101e6bf362b","tid":97000,"uid":33995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T13:30:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>呢個版本玩meepo最好<br />\n易玩左好多,只要對面唔counter就好易贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n是咪不停分身個隻<br />\n比佢屈過機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n不停分身個隻應該係Phantom Lancer<br />\nmeepo係E隻<br />\n<img src=\"https://hydra-media.cursecdn.com/dota2.gamepedia.com/0/03/Meepo.png?version=9e06da86a98ce5ef920561228f7680d1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhydra-media.cursecdn.com%2Fdota2.gamepedia.com%2F0%2F03%2FMeepo.png%3Fversion%3D9e06da86a98ce5ef920561228f7680d1&h=208a5b2c&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n但係我見到呢隻又係不停分身 點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲有點分真身？lol無咁多分身好易分得出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f0450b2b515faa8c88d8a6e4c2986d5d77a05d5","tid":97000,"uid":33995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T13:34:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n不停分身個隻應該係Phantom Lancer<br />\nmeepo係E隻<br />\n<img src=\"https://hydra-media.cursecdn.com/dota2.gamepedia.com/0/03/Meepo.png?version=9e06da86a98ce5ef920561228f7680d1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhydra-media.cursecdn.com%2Fdota2.gamepedia.com%2F0%2F03%2FMeepo.png%3Fversion%3D9e06da86a98ce5ef920561228f7680d1&h=208a5b2c&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n2k 場見到依隻自動輸</blockquote><br />\n對家定自家先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nE個版本真係一個練佢既好日子(自帶吸血,閃避,龍心,A杖)<br />\n特別係冇咩人識counter佢<br />\nfarm個20-30分鐘就無敵</blockquote><br />\n佢係鬥士嗰種屈機？類似lol嘅易大師？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n新手易唔易上手？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1837c6a175a87458ac26456422213c8e4c4819ae","tid":97000,"uid":33995,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T13:36:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n對家定自家先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nE個版本真係一個練佢既好日子(自帶吸血,閃避,龍心,A杖)<br />\n特別係冇咩人識counter佢<br />\nfarm個20-30分鐘就無敵</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打係應該高階場打<br />\n係2k meepo 永遠肥唔起</blockquote><br />\n我都係3-4k場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n打中單<br />\n除非對面好針對(1lv orge/bh掛你機,封曬你D野etc),唔係就好易肥<br />\n今個patch有火鍋去補