ter佢<br />\nfarm個20-30分鐘就無敵</blockquote><br />\n佢係鬥士嗰種屈機？類似lol嘅易大師？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n新手易唔易上手？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n算係dota頭3難玩既英"},{"pid":"a4bc1e92cc93dc9fec9e68c586b5ebabd047b28b","tid":97000,"uid":33511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T13:56:11.000Z","msg":"術士主sup使唔使出四巨人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1db0cf1e41feae14f3a049c74d00c65246cf390","tid":97000,"uid":33511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T13:56:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>術士主sup使唔使出四巨人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nwarlock"},{"pid":"f92a242a4a6354069461f2a1a29501208022b7ba","tid":97000,"uid":73404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T13:57:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>術士主sup使唔使出四巨人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nwarlock</blockquote><br />\n有錢先算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 起碼都出晒glimmer cape 推推捧先"},{"pid":"de1a8662fd35afcaabe14431dde7e2ec449ff032","tid":97000,"uid":78234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T14:00:54.000Z","msg":"隻野唔識分身<br />\n但佢大技每1lv係可以多一隻繼承屬性,天賦,鞋而且可以打錢吸經用技能既分身<br />\n但係只要有任何一隻死,佢其他分身/真身都會死亡(仲會比好多錢+經你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n你見佢不停分身應該係佢招2技,可以直接傳到去任何分身/真身到<br />\n好似我上邊甘講,呢個patch係練佢既好機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但如果新手,D concept未搞清楚就最好唔玩佢(我新手個時玩佢,唔服氣,連輸左十幾場,係甘死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n隻英屈機既位係少人識counter佢,同埋滾雪球超超超超超超超快(分身可以打錢吸經,姐係等於3lv  2隻英,10lv 3隻英既farm 速度,所以可以趁對面隻carry仲唔知發生咩事既情況下end佢game)<br />\n<br />\n火鍋係今個patch新加,唔係裝泥,你咪見你mid lane/offlane/高地附近有D野禁完可以回血回魔既,dire就紅色,radiant就白色,我同D fd叫佢地做麻辣火鍋,同清湯火鍋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\n上高姐係上對面高地既意思<br />\n<br />\nrosh係一隻好似lol大龍既野,打完有好多經,全隊加錢,同一件掉落品(p.s.無buff)<br />\n個件掉落品就係rosh盾,可以比你5min內死一次後可以原地滿血滿魔復活"},{"pid":"01f5cfe5c203757f5c93ccdfb48818a78d55df12","tid":97000,"uid":11319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T14:09:53.000Z","msg":"巴打留個acct 一齊打喇"},{"pid":"08d2403d41afd3e77a899b0ecbe5a8ec0d7255c1","tid":97000,"uid":11319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T14:13:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n對家定自家先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nE個版本真係一個練佢既好日子(自帶吸血,閃避,龍心,A杖)<br />\n特別係冇咩人識counter佢<br />\nfarm個20-30分鐘就無敵</blockquote><br />\n佢係鬥士嗰種屈機？類似lol嘅易大師？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n新手易唔易上手？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n算係dota頭3難玩既英</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n絕對係第一難玩<br />\nchen 同invoker 都唔夠佢多野撳"},{"pid":"3c90b07a8d19495c1ef83e883e38a55af575f7b9","tid":97000,"uid":12518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T14:16:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"deb5e3d966808b2b512a09f577d68d6d5ae6aa4f","tid":97000,"uid":33511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T14:31:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>術士主sup使唔使出四巨人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nwarlock</blockquote><br />\n有錢先算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 起碼都出晒glimmer cape 推推捧先</blockquote><br />\nglimmer cape好難掌握<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbtw操作巨人點先可以無咁拿西<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> default係咪得F1同tab, 好難搞"},{"pid":"83a7733957bb70d5a13fa8e6491c6de853360b7e","tid":97000