re":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T15:19:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>隻野唔識分身<br />\n但佢大技每1lv係可以多一隻繼承屬性,天賦,鞋而且可以打錢吸經用技能既分身<br />\n但係只要有任何一隻死,佢其他分身/真身都會死亡(仲會比好多錢+經你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n你見佢不停分身應該係佢招2技,可以直接傳到去任何分身/真身到<br />\n好似我上邊甘講,呢個patch係練佢既好機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但如果新手,D concept未搞清楚就最好唔玩佢(我新手個時玩佢,唔服氣,連輸左十幾場,係甘死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n隻英屈機既位係少人識counter佢,同埋滾雪球超超超超超超超快(分身可以打錢吸經,姐係等於3lv  2隻英,10lv 3隻英既farm 速度,所以可以趁對面隻carry仲唔知發生咩事既情況下end佢game)<br />\n<br />\n火鍋係今個patch新加,唔係裝泥,你咪見你mid lane/offlane/高地附近有D野禁完可以回血回魔既,dire就紅色,radiant就白色,我同D fd叫佢地做麻辣火鍋,同清湯火鍋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\n上高姐係上對面高地既意思<br />\n<br />\nrosh係一隻好似lol大龍既野,打完有好多經,全隊加錢,同一件掉落品(p.s.無buff)<br />\n個件掉落品就係rosh盾,可以比你5min內死一次後可以原地滿血滿魔復活</blockquote><br />\n學到野了 多謝巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7869a344b883ee488b4ee58ac2d176a6e8f70627","tid":97000,"uid":33995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T15:23:25.000Z","msg":"到依家主要玩 Pudge PA Sven Monkey King呢幾隻 有無類似風格又適合新手用嘅英雄？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3bd9482913d6d363fbd08fc6d4b5cd235c09390","tid":97000,"uid":33995,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T15:27:59.000Z","msg":"仲有到底反捕條件係點？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8344f13fc8013682babcf6a48bb133fcc061838","tid":97000,"uid":11115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T15:43:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>玩左1個月左右開始接觸ranked