ets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n依度不嬲大把神手"},{"pid":"289f73aa52d870665fcee9caee41398cc416419e","tid":97000,"uid":11319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T17:10:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>到依家主要玩 Pudge PA Sven Monkey King呢幾隻 有無類似風格又適合新手用嘅英雄？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n除左Pudge 其他都係carry <br />\n如果你想打carry 玩劍聖 sven 拍拍熊 會爽啲<br />\npa 有時黑仔十年都唔暴"},{"pid":"76651a056c9d5e2a7bb7d24a06b4f5bcc7accefb","tid":97000,"uid":30768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T00:33:52.000Z","msg":"我都係新手，有冇啲咩英特別適合新手玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dca38961399c310757bed05a0347dc70e7684c55","tid":97000,"uid":56465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T01:01:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都係新手，有冇啲咩英特別適合新手玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\ncarry : OD,Luna,jugg,sevn,usha,weaver <br />\noffline:cg, centaur, timber, underlord <br />\nsupport:WD,lion,Enigma,bane"},{"pid":"4aa1ef6a3d25ad51d7b3dd754ff1b64c8ec37f5e","tid":97000,"uid":30768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T01:07:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我都係新手，有冇啲咩英特別適合新手玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\ncarry : OD,Luna,jugg,sevn,usha,weaver <br />\noffline:cg, centaur, timber, underlord <br />\nsupport:WD,lion,Enigma,bane</blockquote><br />\n我打normal成日都有人送頭，係唔係我問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b6388eb9cb614d2aeafe5be99c208551863da4b","tid":97000,"uid":56465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T02:17:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我都係新手，有冇啲咩英特別適合新手玩<